{"Title":"糖渍橙皮的做法","Primary":["橙皮4个","冰糖150克"],"Auxiliary":["柠檬1/2个","砂糖适量"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.橙子用温水浸泡30分钟","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/238/152/2913238/n2913238_142249383484222.jpg","2.用盐把外面的蜡去掉，多擦几遍","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/238/152/2913238/n2913238_142249384159000.jpg","3.把橙子切成小块","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/238/152/2913238/n2913238_142249384949293.jpg","4.把橙子肉剥出来，橙皮备用","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/238/152/2913238/n2913238_142249385304714.jpg","5.用小刀把白色部分清除掉","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/238/152/2913238/n2913238_142249385927463.jpg","6.把处理好的橙皮切小条放温水里浸泡半天，每隔一段时间换次水","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/238/152/2913238/n2913238_142249386934061.jpg","7.冰糖加适量水煮到融化","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/238/152/2913238/n2913238_142249387876893.jpg","8.把浸泡好的橙皮放入锅里，加半个柠檬汁","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/238/152/2913238/n2913238_142249388453675.jpg","9.煮到汁水收干橙皮变透明，边煮边搅拌","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/238/152/2913238/n2913238_142249389122546.jpg","10.取出后摊开放凉","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/238/152/2913238/n2913238_142249389771840.jpg","11.裹上砂糖即可","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/238/152/2913238/n2913238_142249390367085.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/238/152/2913238/n2913238_142249391511385.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/238/152/2913238/n2913238_142249392665439.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/238/152/2913238/n2913238_142249393010202.jpg","烹饪技巧","　　橙皮的白色部分去干净点！浸泡时间长点就没有口味了！"]}